And as always check your status and your fellow Trump supporter contacts frequently in the next 30 days: https://www.usa.gov/state-election-office

We are committed to ensuring our friends and family make to the polls, rain, sleet, or shine. Block your calendars, reschedule your meetings. Nothing matters more on November 5th than the future of America.

Take action by forming your own Get out the Vote plan or volunteering by signing up at https://trumpforce47.com

Sign-up to be a Poll-Worker https://patriots.win/p/17txRDHXhQ/maga-pollworker-megathread-v2/
